This is a shopping website with a Next 13 app router.
The purpose is to provide the possibility of user authentication by OTP and httpOnly cookie with a refresh token and access token.
The Admin can view, add, and edit products, categories, orders, coupons, and users in his panel.
The user can view and order the products, pay from his cart, and see the orders in his panel.
using OTP for authentication and authorization in the admin and user panels.
using technologies: react-query, axios, and tailwind CSS.
includes ssr, ssg, and csr pages.

you must add .env in server with this properties:

APP_DB=mongodb://0.0.0.0:27017/next-shop
KAVENEGAR_API_KEY=YOU_SHOULD_GET_YOUROWN_KEY
ACCESS_TOKEN_SECRET_KEY=EREWRDr3423$_%^$@jghbhgNBVN@@@^&^%35
REFRESH_TOKEN_SECRET_KEY=DDDDDDFHGSAEWQEFRHGJYTRREwe123!@!!@^&^%^
COOKIE_PARSER_SECRET_KEY=fdGEWREGRTsdfdkjasfaDS2323~@~!23426*
TOKEN_SECRET_KEY=sdvasdnfdfsafGHJHKer~@@!$$$^%&^&^*@HgJGJ
ZARINPAL_CALLBACK_URL=/api/payment/verify
CLIENT_URL=http://localhost:3000
SERVER_URL=http://localhost:5000
NODE_ENV=development
PORT=5000
ALLOW_CORS_ORIGIN=http://localhost:3000

you must add .env.local in client with this properties:

NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:5000/api
NODE_ENV=development
